494
00:34:15,060 --> 00:34:16,960
so that you can enjoy it when I get the chance.

495
00:34:16,960 --> 00:34:18,389
I'm no longer interested in

496
00:34:18,389 --> 00:34:20,190
spirit fruits.

497
00:34:20,710 --> 00:34:21,790
Right now,

498
00:34:22,850 --> 00:34:25,400
