00:38:51,240 --> 00:38:52,770
How dare you touch me?

574
00:38:53,530 --> 00:38:55,530
You won't even address me politely.

575
00:38:55,810 --> 00:38:56,850
How rude!

576
00:39:33,620 --> 00:39:34,530
Let them go.

577
00:39:35,070 --> 00:39:36,510
I can let them go,

578
00:39:37,050 --> 00:39:38,470
as long as you

579
00:39:38,710 --> 00:39:39,990
hand over your pearl.

580
00:39:42,350 --> 00:39:43,800
Why do you want my pearl?

581
00:39:44,500 --> 00:39:45,870
It's all because of you self-proclaimed

582
00:39:45,870 --> 00:39:47,170
righteous cultivators that have forced

583
00:39:47,170 --> 00:39:49,300
our Demon Clan into such dire straits.

584
00:39:49,910 --> 00:39:51,350
As the dignified elder of the Evil Path,

585
00:39:51,350 --> 00:39:52,750
I even have to hide my true identity

586
00:39:52,750 --> 00:39:55,880
and disguise myself as a boat owner to lurk in the market.

587
00:39:56,550 --> 00:39:57,150
But if

588
00:39:57,150 --> 00:39:58,560
I have your pearl,

589
00:39:58,940 --> 00:40:01,200
I can conceal my presence at any time,

590
00:40:01,920 --> 00:40:03,520
and come and go freely

591
00:40:03,910 --> 00:40:05,980
within the five states.

592
00:40:06,200 --> 00:40:07,900
No, you can't give it to her.

593
00:40:08,230 --> 00:40:09,310
Who knows how many lives

594
00:40:09,310 --> 00:40:10,070
will she harm

595
00:40:10,150 --> 00:40:11,480
once she has your pearl?

596
00:40:15,470 --> 00:40:17,230
You'd better think carefully.

597
00:40:17,830 --> 00:40:19,210
Is the life of these two young masters

598
00:40:19,210 --> 00:40:20,140
more important,

599
00:40:21,420 --> 00:40:23,160
or your pearl?

